## Onchain Testing

**Start Anvil Fork**

```bash
anvil --fork-url https://0xrpc.io/sep --chain-id 11155111 --auto-impersonate
```

**Test Contract Call**

```bash
cast call 0x3bbDcC93e2E3dcDF9984afb5AEBaa3de52FE5591 \
  --data  \
  --trace \
  --rpc-url http://localhost:8545 \
  --from 0x83c1C2a52d56dFb958C52831a3D683cFAfC34c75 \
  --etherscan-api-key 3KUNX1YPQVW51NP78JSA57PNC6VPTGGDM9
```
